PackageEtherCaptureDemo is a minimum-size project to demonstrate using PackageEtherCapture to capture packets.

By hardcoding interface "en0" and command "icmp or icmp6" we capture packets on the commmand-line with less than 10 lines of source code.

Related repositories:

PackageEtherCapture
etherdump-CLI (full feature CLI packet capture tool)
Etherdump (full feature GUI packet capture tool)
